Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.42,0:00:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,个人翻译作品请勿用于商业用途 初次翻译诸多错误还望见谅\N@嘉鱼鱼鱼鱼鱼鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.88,0:00:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 非常感谢\NThank you. Thanks very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.99,0:00:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,女士们 先生们 今晚我带来了一位朋友\NAnd ladies and gentlemen, I have a friend here tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.01,0:00:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,和我一样 她离开家乡来到这\Nwho like me, she's a long way from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.30,0:00:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们不介意的话\NAnd if it's ok with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.00,0:00:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想你们要不要让她唱首她的歌?\NI was wondering if you'd like her to play one of her songs?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.86,0:00:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗?好吗?\NIs that okay? Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.54,0:01:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Gretta 能请你上来吗?\NGretta, will you come up here please?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等一下\NAhh, just give me a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得这会是个很好的主意\NI think it'd be a really good idea
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.65,0:01:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你能上来唱一首你的歌\Nif you'd come up here and sing one of your songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.99,0:01:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为这是一个很糟糕的主意\NI think it'd be a really fucking bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.32,0:01:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 来吧 Gretta 这可是纽约 - 不要!\N- Gretta, come on. This is New York. - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.93,0:01:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都想听的 对吧?\NYou want to hear it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.53,0:01:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定会超棒的\NYou're gonna be amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.00,0:01:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 这是一首新歌 所以可能会有点粗糙\NHi, ah, so this is a new song it might be kind of rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.80,0:01:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,献给城市中所有寂寞的人们\NIt's for anyone who's ever been alone in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.41,0:01:44.41,顶部,,0,0,0,,{\c&H3B9CD4&\i1\1a&H00&}A Step You Can't Take Back - Keira Knightley{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.41,0:01:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}你发现自己在地铁里\NSo you find yourself at this subway{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.33,0:01:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}当你的世界在包装下 随身携带\NWhen your world in a bag by your side{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.12,0:02:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}一切似乎看起来很完美\NAnd all at once it seemed like a good way{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.79,0:02:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}你意识到这就是你生命的终结\NYou realized its the end of your life{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.82,0:02:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}意义也就如此\NFor what it's worth{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.99,0:02:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}火车在轨道上奔驰而来\NHere comes the train upon the track{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.71,0:02:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}带走伤痛只剩下一片黑\NAnd there goes the pain it cuts to black{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.04,0:02:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}最后的行动你准备好了吗?\NAre you ready for the last act?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.68,0:02:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}踏上永不回头的征程\NTo take a step you can't take back{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.13,0:02:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}她爱你吗?\NDid she love you?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.96,0:02:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}她带给你伤痛吗?\NDid she take you down?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.92,0:02:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}在亲吻你的王冠时\NWas she on her knees{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.92,0:02:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}她有没有双膝跪地?\Nwhen she kissed your crown?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}告诉我你所知道的\NTell me what you found{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.86,0:03:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}大雨不期而至 抓紧你的帽子\NHere comes the rain, so hold your hat{\i}
