Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.40,0:47:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你再决定要不要让我滚蛋行么\NAnd then you can tell me to fuck myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.83,0:47:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是别人给我们寄来音乐样本\NPeople send us their demos.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.79,0:47:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是反过来的 我们又不负责出小样\NIt's not the other way around. We don't make demos.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.10,0:47:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是制作人 我们也是投资人\NWe're prospectors man. We're investors.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.26,0:47:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就像是在挖金矿\NWe're digging for gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.67,0:47:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,先去录个小样吧 然后拿来再让我听听\NMake a tape and we'll get back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.92,0:47:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟 我能做的也只有这些了\NThat's the best I can do right now, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.34,0:47:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 我在想啊\NSo, I've been thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.66,0:47:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我们要租个一个录音棚?\NWhy do we even need to rent a fucking studio?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.13,0:47:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你需要桌子 器材 还有隔音装备?\NBecause you need a desk, a live room and sound proofing.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.30,0:47:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,也就需要笔记本电脑 Pro Tools软件和几个麦克风\NLaptop. Pro Tools. A couple of dynamic mics.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.14,0:47:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这城市就是我们的演播室\NAnd the city is our fucking live room.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.78,0:47:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你指在室外录音?\NYou mean record outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.89,0:47:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没错 - 哪呢?\N- That's right. - Like where?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.74,0:47:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,到处都可以\NEverywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.80,0:47:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,别管他!\NFuck him.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.85,0:47:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也不做小样了 直接做个专辑!\NWe don't need a demo. Let's record an album.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.60,0:47:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,一首歌找一个地方\NEvery song we do in a different location.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.65,0:47:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就在纽约找就行\NAll over New York City.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.17,0:47:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,找个夏天就能开始做\NAnd we do it through the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.77,0:48:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,就献给这个\NAnd it becomes this tribute to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.92,0:48:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,美丽 疯狂又混乱的城市--纽约\Nbeautiful, god damn crazy, fractured mess of a city, New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.74,0:48:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊 比如在东区的桥下\NOK. Under the bridge on the lower east side.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.74,0:48:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,帝国大厦的顶层\NTop of the Empire State building.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.91,0:48:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,中央公园湖水的船上\NOn rowing boats in the lake in Central Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.10,0:48:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,唐人街 圣约翰大教堂\NChinatown. Cathedral of Saint John the Divine
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.44,0:48:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,还有地铁 哈姆雷区 在哪儿都行\NIn the subway. Fucking Harlem. Everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.91,0:48:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,如果下雨怎么办\NSo what happens if it starts raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.79,0:48:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,无论发生什么 都继续录下来\NWhatever happens, we record it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.44,0:48:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们被逮捕了呢?\NIf we get arrested?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.71,0:48:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,继续录啊!那太赞了!\NKeep rolling! It'll be beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.35,0:48:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢么?\NYou like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.47,0:48:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么想?很不错吧\NWhat do you think? It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.89,0:48:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你会帮我来制作么? - 我? - 恩\N- Will you produce it? - Me? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.72,0:48:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经好久没做过了\NI haven't produced in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.85,0:48:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我会找个年轻点的来做\NWe'll get somebody young to produce it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.85,0:48:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不 我想要你来做 - 为什么?\N- No, but I want you to do it. - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.60,0:48:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是想让你来\NBecause I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.68,0:48:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我有弦乐器 但我们很需要个钢琴 然后还有吉他\NI give you strings, but we definitely need piano. Then with the guitars underneath.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.72,0:48:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的 我喜欢 - 好的 - 好的\N- Got it. I love it. - Done. - Done.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.79,0:48:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,世界第一辆捷豹手机音乐工作室诞生了\NThe world's first Jag mobile recording studio. It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.57,0:48:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,太有才了!\NIt's bloody genius it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.14,0:48:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪儿?\NWhere do you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.57,0:48:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要些音乐人\NWe need musicians.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.43,0:49:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,无聊又悲惨的音乐人\NTerminally, miserably bored musicians.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.28,0:49:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,之后我觉得...\NAfter that I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.93,0:49:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你先弹奏小提琴和大提琴 先大提琴再小提琴\Nthen you bring in the violin and cello. First cello then violin.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.18,0:49:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,直到主音吉他响起来的时候 我想把它混成不同的声音效果\NWhen we get into that lead guitar thing, I want it to become\Na whole different kind of sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.64,0:49:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这个是Malcolm 他是个神童\NThis is Malcolm. Malcolm is a child prodigy.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.83,0:49:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他从五岁就开始拉小提琴了\NHe's been playing violin since he was five years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.82,0:49:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 确切的说是我从四岁就开始了 - 四岁\N- I technically started when I was four. - Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.75,0:49:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这是他的姐姐Rachel\NAnd this is his older sister, Rachel.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.83,0:49:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,她就读于曼哈顿音乐学院 还拿全额奖学金\NShe's at the Manhattan School of Music on a full scholarship.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.82,0:49:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们班最出色的大提琴手 - 这太棒了\N- Top of her class cellist. - That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.20,0:49:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,事情是这样的\NSo here's the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.52,0:49:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我没法先付给你们工资\NI can't afford to pay you up front.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.28,0:49:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 我想和你们先签合同 之后再付钱给你们\NSo I want to offer you a legitimate back end deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.88,0:49:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗?\NSound good?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.16,0:49:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 只要它不是什么狗屁古典音乐就行\NYeah, as long as it's not fucking Vivaldi.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.28,0:49:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,当然不会是那破玩意儿\NIt's not fucking Vivaldi.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.67,0:49:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不错 不 不 这太赞了\NIt's great. No, no, no. It's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.86,0:49:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 必须有钢琴声 在吉他的部分切入\NDefinitely need piano. Like fill in the guitar underneath.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.87,0:49:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 你说的对\NYou got it. I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.26,0:50:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Steve 太美丽了\NSteve, beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.03,0:50:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- Zach 这是干什么? - 我不干了 - 姑娘们 祝你们好运 - 保持联系\N- Zach. What's going on? - I quit. - Good lucks, girls. - Keep in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.88,0:50:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,吉他的下一段\NWhen we get into that lead guitar thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.30,0:50:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我想把它混成不同的声音效果\NI want it to become a whole different kind of sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.87,0:50:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要那种朋克加上流行音乐的那种感觉\NI want it to be punk meets pop.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.40,0:50:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨起来!\NAnd have some fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.63,0:50:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他到了\NAh, he's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.24,0:51:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Dan 还好么 兄弟?\NDan, what's up, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.43,0:51:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Troublegum 我的兄弟 有了你什么都解决了\NTroublegum, my brother. My troubles are over.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.69,0:51:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,还给我客气什么啊\NWhat say you give me some love, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.83,0:51:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这里了!这里简直是帮派的天堂啊 看到你真高兴\NThis is it! Gangsta paradise. I'm glad to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.34,0:51:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 虽然我不认识你 但还是让我来抱一下\NThanks to you. Give me a hug. I don' t know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.56,0:51:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这是Gretta\NThat's Gretta.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.37,0:51:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒的歌手 作曲人\NGreat singer and songwriter.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.72,0:51:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 再抱一下 - 再一个?\N- Let's get another one. - Another one? Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.52,0:51:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你都哪儿了?这都两三年没见了\NWhere have you been? It's been two or years.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.61,0:51:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我一点也不喜欢这样\NI don't appreciate this shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.71,0:51:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,停滞不前的 做点这个 做点那个呗\NBeen on the down low a little bit. Doing this. Doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.88,0:51:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,等待一个新的机会\NWaiting for the next move.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.35,0:51:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,期待着再一次的最佳状态\NAnticipating the next groove.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.98,0:51:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你想证明些什么 是吧?\NI know you got a lot of shit to prove, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.46,0:51:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,私下里 找寻着那一个好声音\NBeen on the underground, looking for that new sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.08,0:51:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可不能再徘徊下去了\NWe ain't fucking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.92,0:51:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是对是错\N'Cause if it ain't right then it's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.87,0:51:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,路还长\NAnd the road is long
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.96,0:51:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,下一步走出前\Nand you're only as strong
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.96,0:51:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你会知道你自己有多强大\Nas your next move.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.73,0:51:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 感觉对么? - 挺对的\N- You feel that? - That's pretty much it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.74,0:51:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这就像什么超自然现象一样\NDamn. That was like some paranormal activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.27,0:51:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,反正你懂我的\NYou know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.37,0:52:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我真是太高兴见到你了 老兄 Jimmy 你把刚刚那词儿记下来了没? - 放心 记下了\N- I'm just so happy to see you, man. Yo! Fat Jimmy, did you get that down? - Yeah, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.51,0:52:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚那一段儿真够棒的 宝贝儿 来 拉着我手\N'Cause that was exceptionally good. Hold my hand, baby. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.01,0:52:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,老兄 我该怎么帮你?\NHow can I help you, brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.60,0:52:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,一个户外的专辑!这主意太赞了!\NAn outdoor album! That's fucking crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.13,0:52:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么就想不到这么棒的主意呢 你想要我做什么?\NI wish I could have thought of that. What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.60,0:52:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要的音乐人 我还需要贝司手和鼓手\NI need musicians. I need a base player and a drummer.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.57,0:52:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我这儿音乐人多着呢\NI got plenty of musicians.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.78,0:52:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,问题是我们没钱请他们\NThe problem is we can't pay them.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.92,0:52:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 管他呢 我来付钱就行了 - 为什么?\N- Fuck it. I'll pay them. - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.88,0:52:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,什么为什么?我这是为了他\NWhat do you mean why? For him.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.42,0:52:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\NOf course.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.33,0:52:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 来吧 跳进泳池吧 - 别碰我 小心我杀了你\N- Come on. Get your sexy self in the pool. - No. Don't touch me. I will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.10,0:52:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,她是英国人 有些保守\NShe's English. She's a little uptight.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.11,0:52:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- Gretta 我祝你专辑一切顺利 - 谢谢\N- Good luck on the album, Gretta. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.20,0:52:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你看这儿的别墅 跑车什么的\NEverything you see around here. This crib. These cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.86,0:52:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,都是因为他\NThey're because of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.59,0:52:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我永远不会忘记的 - 我明白了 - 不 不 不\N- I don't ever forget that. - I get it. - No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.31,0:52:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你可不会了解的\NYou can't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.28,0:52:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,像他那样的人 出名几年后\NA guy like that falls on his luck for a couple of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.24,0:52:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,人们压根就不会记得他是谁\NPeople lose sight of who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.24,0:53:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,人们不尊重他 但他确实值得我们尊重\NAnd they don't treat him with the respect. He deserves.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.78,0:53:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他说的都是废话\NAnything he's saying is bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.14,0:53:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,有事就来联系我\NAnything you need, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.47,0:53:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我太爱你了 感谢你\NI love you, man. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.01,0:53:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢她\NI like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.73,0:53:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定么?这儿的杂音你听见了么?\NAre you serious? Are you listening to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.62,0:53:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要把杂音用进去 会很棒的\NWe're gonna use it. It's gonna be genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.16,0:53:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是个天才 我不用担心的\NYou're a genius. I don't have any fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.29,0:53:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你听不见我都听到了些什么\NYou don't hear what I hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.13,0:53:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你会让我脑中的音乐变成现实的\NYou're gonna make it real. I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.71,0:53:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,开始吧?\NGot it?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.70,0:53:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 音轨里全是那群孩子的声音 - 你说什么?\N- Those kids are gonna be all over this track. - What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.45,0:53:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我拿下这个\NTake this.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.13,0:53:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,小屁孩们 来来来\NLittle children. Yo! Yo! Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.53,0:53:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰一下啊\NLet me see this for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.80,0:53:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我正在录制一首歌\NI'm shooting a song down here
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.79,0:53:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 能帮我个忙 安静五分钟吗? - 没门\N- and I need you guys to be quiet for five minutes? - No way, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.36,0:53:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我给钱\NI'll pay you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.45,0:53:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 多少? - 每人一美元\N- How much? - A buck each.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.77,0:54:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你真搞笑 五块钱\NHey, you're funny. Five dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.24,0:54:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是给你们所有人五块钱嘛?好吧 两块钱! 每个孩子两块钱\NFive bucks for all of you guys? Okay. Two bucks! Two bucks each.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.62,0:54:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不!\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.33,0:54:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好 每人五美元\NAll right. Five bucks each.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.17,0:54:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那你给我们每个人五块钱和五个棒棒糖\NBring us five bucks and five lollipops. One for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.67,0:54:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,或者一包香烟和打火机也行\NThrow in a box of cigarettes and lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.65,0:54:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你们所有人一包烟 你们分着抽\NI'll give you one cigarette for each of you to smoke and you share it.
