Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.30,0:56:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样!就是这样!\NYes! Yes! That was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.05,0:56:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,简直太棒了!\NYes! It's gonna work!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.14,0:56:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊!那就是帝国大厦嘛?\NOh my God! Is that the Empire State?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.15,0:56:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 就是这儿\NYeah, right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.85,0:57:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们摆在这里 然后站在那里 - 非常好 - 是啊\NSet up here. Get that. - It's really good. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.98,0:57:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 太棒了 - 风会不会有问题?\N- Great. - The wind's good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.44,0:57:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不算特别响 没事的\NIt's not too loud. It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.75,0:57:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,还可以看见别人家的窗口 真是太有趣了\NAnd we can look into people's windows, which is always fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.96,0:57:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你想跟我一起去接Violet吗? - 可以吗? - 可以啊 走吧\N- You want to come with me to get Violet? - Is that Okay? - Yeah. Come on.
